Gonna start with the meat
curry along with the okra.

00:07:57.260 --> 00:07:59.563
Wow, that has some oily goodness to it.

00:08:01.238 --> 00:08:02.488
- Cheers, dude.

00:08:07.735 --> 00:08:09.860
- Oh yeah, you could
just tell from his smile

00:08:09.860 --> 00:08:14.860
and his, like, jolly aura that
his food was gonna be good.

00:08:15.070 --> 00:08:17.921
Oh, that's just warm and
comforting and rich and delicious.

00:08:17.921 --> 00:08:19.910
Very nice.
- Okay, okay.

00:08:19.910 --> 00:08:20.860
- [Mark] Thank you.

00:08:22.875 --> 00:08:24.602
It's got that wonderful, like, sliminess

00:08:24.602 --> 00:08:26.098
from the okra.

00:08:26.098 --> 00:08:28.348
(laughing)

