so he set it on the table with us.

00:08:40.369 --> 00:08:41.202
(laughing)

00:08:41.202 --> 00:08:44.012
Gave us a big smile and thumbs
up while he was doing it.

00:08:44.012 --> 00:08:45.580
(laughing)

00:08:45.580 --> 00:08:46.710
What an amazing man.

00:08:46.710 --> 00:08:47.960
Oh man, you can smell that.

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:51.060
The coriander seed is what
always is so noticeable to me,

00:08:51.060 --> 00:08:53.619
and this is all buffalo
meat, made from buffalo meat.

00:08:53.619 --> 00:08:55.157
Okay, beautiful.

