That's one of the greatest
possible formations of meat.

00:09:03.176 --> 00:09:05.780
(woman speaking in foreign language)

00:09:05.780 --> 00:09:06.960
Yes.

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:10.143
Okay, we're probably spending
way too much time here.

00:09:11.157 --> 00:09:14.680
We could just not leave,
but we gotta move on,

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:16.430
because we gotta get to the village

