The bridge actually leads
across, this is the Hunza River.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:36.440
Oh, man, the peaks, the snow-capped peaks,

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:39.223
just fully surrounding, it's spectacular.

00:09:40.329 --> 00:09:42.131
