People wanted to shake hands,

00:09:58.340 --> 00:10:00.670
dish they have a photo, to smile.

00:10:00.670 --> 00:10:03.173
Yeah, people are amazing here.

00:10:03.173 --> 00:10:05.756
(upbeat music)

00:10:12.537 --> 00:10:15.460
(speaking in foreign language)

