One of Ali's employees
is from this village,

00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:19.280
and he invited us to his village,

00:10:19.280 --> 00:10:20.983
to his home, for lunch today.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:25.220
That's the backyard,
that's their backyard.

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:26.890
Look at that peak, you could just...

00:10:26.890 --> 00:10:29.513
The mist, spectacular scenery.

00:10:30.930 --> 00:10:32.130
Nizam is the...

00:10:32.130 --> 00:10:33.730
He's hosting us.

